Invocation Name: weird haiku
des:
Are you a fan of surrealist poetry? You'll love Weird Haku. Contemporary Japanese haiku and the poems of American surrealist poet Charles Henri Ford serve as inspiration for this haiku reader. 

Embrace the surreal with 17 original haikus. Want to contribute your own Weird Haiku? Send your submission to info@vekkr.com

Here are a few examples of what you can say:

Alexa, start Weird Haiku.
Alexa, run Weird Haiku.
Alexa, open Weird Haiku.
